18:06.117 --> 18:08.252
and like,
in the middle of the interview,

18:08.286 --> 18:09.922
the interviewer stopped it
and said, "Oh,

18:09.954 --> 18:13.125
"they just shut down, like,
the city of Wuhan

18:13.157 --> 18:16.127
<i>and there's no more transport
