We were told the CDC was
working diligently on a test,

19:28.767 --> 19:32.537
and we were relying
solely on the CDC.

19:32.569 --> 19:36.107
<i>I raised the need to get
started immediately</i>

19:36.140 --> 19:39.143
<i>on commercial test development
drugs and vaccines,</i>

