<i>and the need for money
to do it.</i>

19:42.113 --> 19:44.616
<i>The secretary looked at me</i>

19:44.648 --> 19:47.084
<i>and said, "You need money?"</i>

19:47.117 --> 19:49.687
And I said,
"Yes, we've exercised

19:49.721 --> 19:53.525
<i>that it would take
about $10 billion."</i>

19:53.558 --> 19:57.261
<i>Without that experience
and knowledge,</i>

19:57.294 --> 19:58.629
<i>I might not have walked
into that room</i>

19:58.663 --> 20:00.565
<i>and asked for those things,</i>

20:00.598 --> 20:02.832
but I knew exactly
what was needed.

20:02.834 --> 20:06.238
<i>I learned after
that meeting, actually,</i>

20:06.271 --> 20:09.074
<i>that a lot of the people
were pretty offended</i>

20:09.107 --> 20:11.143
<i>that I would come into
a meeting with the Secretary</i>

20:11.175 --> 20:14.245
<i>on day one and ask for money.</i>

