<i>By January 27th,</i>

24:13.050 --> 24:15.787
<i>South Korea was on its way
to containing the virus</i>

24:15.819 --> 24:17.856
<i>and preventing
an economic shutdown.</i>

24:21.925 --> 24:23.528
Good morning, everyone.

24:23.560 --> 24:27.064
